{"tid":2478757,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"受不了社會主義鐵拳  中国動漫迷入侵台灣","createTime":"2021-04-07T09:47:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T10:08:04.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dc93967f6ec32a09d5dc678f89741a5ab0d6bae7","tid":2478757,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:47:15.000Z","msg":"中國廣電總局的「先審後播」新政策讓自家動漫迷們群起崩潰，紛紛尋找避難之處，只為了能繼續追新番。而除了Bilibili（B站）的台港澳分區可以使用VPN跳轉後觀看以外，台灣最為知名的ACG論壇巴哈姆特動畫瘋竟意外成為中國動漫迷「最後一片淨土」。<br />\n<br />\n在中國廣電總局針對境外動畫下達登記並通過審查後才能播放的命令後，導致不少原訂4月開始播放的新番迄今在B站「完全沒有畫面」。俗話說「上有政策，下有對策」，此舉也致使不少對岸的動漫迷們開始在各大論壇討論要去哪裡避難。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/07/3100695-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F07%2F3100695-PH.jpg&h=23c7a819&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲百度貼吧有人無奈表示「對政策不滿意但支持」。（圖／翻攝自百度貼吧）<br />\n<br />\n綜合上述原因，中國網友除了提及B站設有針對台港澳開放的分區（禁止中國網路IP瀏覽）以外，有大量免費正版動畫的巴哈姆特動畫瘋也成為了「避難首選」，紛紛呼朋引伴翻牆進軍巴哈姆特，不過此舉也引來不少台灣網友反感。<br />\n<br />\n對於中國網友高聲疾呼進駐巴哈姆特動畫瘋的行徑，大多數台灣網友抱持著反對態度，認為彈幕會出現無謂的爭吵，特別是政治的相關言論，希望巴哈姆特官方能從現在開始針對會員身分及網路IP進行嚴格審核，不要讓台灣會員觀影權益受到影響。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/07/3100694-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F07%2F3100694-PH.jpg&h=e24977d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/07/3100696-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F07%2F3100696-PH.jpg&h=ba25ce18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/07/3100693-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F07%2F3100693-PH.jpg&h=cb72625a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲有不少中國網友紛紛搖旗吶喊，進軍巴哈姆特動畫瘋。（圖／翻攝自百度貼吧）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=922068\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D922068&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtFScv4UPbHgCWRxxYzHlmUY%3D&h=c3680827\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D922068&h=a8d8e3d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=922068</a>"},{"pid":"b57d18a4a9f2ec6cc2de9a2d03ec78b977770d81","tid":2478757,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:48:44.000Z","msg":"台灣動畫<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mDV4AQbwCqM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmDV4AQbwCqM&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtFScv4UPbHgCWRxxYzHlmUY%3D&h=659d358f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mDV4AQbwCqM</a>"},{"pid":"30ddbfd8a8408030f1018e52759050c1d7fd8730","tid":2478757,"uid":195169,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:49:59.000Z","msg":"不滿意但支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支持但又犯法，用vpn去台灣睇"},{"pid":"2be91efe9cdaa8f2cfc488ab30a35381d975060d","tid":2478757,"uid":34410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:50:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />班支毒撚又話動漫還動漫，政治還政治既"},{"pid":"1ff14f3d2781ba7095b006fe53bdd95f92aa46c9","tid":2478757,"uid":21432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:53:35.000Z","msg":"如果巴哈唔做野就我地幫佢做，巴哈既播放權應該只限俾台灣地區收看，如果發現支那仔睇到就report俾版權持有人"},{"pid":"4844897f05946f11a4a247dc492b0d86e4a650b0","tid":2478757,"uid":103230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:57:35.000Z","msg":"台灣想應對好簡單<br />\n網站同動畫加晒反共文宣<br />\n<br />\n老共第一日就封網<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"376acc0e7a12c164cad5df1eb5287523e498fea8","tid":2478757,"uid":114781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T10:03:24.000Z","msg":"支那蝗蟲，所到之處，寸草不生<img src=\"/as